ked with penetrating German-held territory and bringing the boy home.','1998-07-24','Saving Private Ryan.jpg','RYExstiQlLc','RandomUser','3','Quality WWII film, gritty and violent','2018-04-26 11:38:27'),(94,'The Room','17473','Johnny is a successful banker with great respect for and dedication to the people in his life, especially his future wife Lisa. The happy-go-lucky guy sees his world fall apart when his friends begin to betray him one-by-one.','2003-06-27','The Room.jpg','pKAwXLVxuZQ','RandomUser','4','Completely Terrible!  and yet, quite wonderful','2018-04-26 11:40:34'),(96,'Inglourious Basterds','16869','In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a group of Jewish-American soldiers known as \"The Basterds\" are chosen specifically to spread fear throughout the Third Reich by scalping and brutally killing Nazis. The Basterds, lead by Lt. Aldo Raine soon cross paths with a French-Jewish teenage girl who runs a movie theater in Paris which is targeted by the soldiers.','2009-08-18','Inglourious Basterds.jpg','-2cRY4p7KIk','RandomUser','4','test','2018-04-26 12:39:31'),(97,'Ready Player One','333339','When the creator of a popular video game system dies, a virtual contest is created to compete for his fortune.','2018-03-28','Ready Player One.jpg','dtwpjnuaVTE','MoviesFan','3','Not as good as the book but I expected that going in.  Decent movie with good visuals.','2018-04-27 00:01:53'),(98,'Blade Runner','78','In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.','1982-06-25','Blade Runner.jpg','PSIiGE105iA','MoviesFan','4','Classic Sci-fi thriller.  This one took some time to grow on me but I eventually learned to appreciate it.','2018-04-27 00:11:40'),(102,'The Truman Show','37165','Truman Burbank is the star of \"The Truman Show\", a 24-hour-a-day \"reality\" TV show that broadcasts every aspect of his life -- live and in color -- without his knowledge. His entire life has been an unending soap opera for consumption by the rest of the world. And everyone he knows -- including his wife and his best friend -- is really an actor, paid to be part of his life.','1998-06-04','The Truman Show.jpg','c3gI9ms8Fdc','MoviesFan','3','Decently funny Jim Carrey movie','2018-04-27 00:22:22'),(103,'Django Unchained','68718','With the help of a German bounty hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal Mississippi plantation owner.','2012-12-25','Django Unchained.jpg','_iH0UBYDI4g','MoviesFan','4','Violent, gripping tale of a slave who is set free then becomes a bounty hunter and eventually frees his wife.  Almost Everyone dies horribly - good times.','2018-04-27 01:42:45'),(104,'Alien','348','During its return to the earth, commercial spaceship Nostromo intercepts a distress signal from a distant planet. When a three-member team of the crew discovers a chamber containing thousands of eggs on the planet, a creature inside one of the eggs attacks an explorer. The entire crew is unaware of the impending nightmare set to descend upon them when the alien parasite planted inside its unfortunate host is birthed.','1979-05-25','Alien.jpg','097uj1HjkbM','RandomUser','3','The original Alien, a true sci-fi masterpiece.  I remember thinking the scene where the android does the thing with his hand and the knife was amazing.','2018-04-27 06:32:36'),(105,'Interstellar','157336','Interstellar chronicles the adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.','2014-11-05','Interstellar.jpg','2LqzF5WauAw','RandomUser','2','I liked it until about 75% of the way through.  It just got too long and he point started to fade.  I liked the way time sped up when they visited the planet close to the black hole.  ','2018-04-27 06:59:30'),(106,'The Martian','286217','During a manned mission to Mars, Astronaut Mark Watney is presumed dead after a fierce storm and left behind by his crew. But Watney has survived and finds himself stranded and alone on the hostile planet. With only meager supplies, he must draw upon his ingenuity, wit and spirit to subsist and find a way to signal to Earth that he is alive.','2015-09-30','The Martian.jpg','Ue4PCI0NamI','RandomUser','4','A good Sci-fi thriller!  Nice visuals with a good story.  I could have done without Matt Damon but he actually did a decent job of not screwing up the movie by being himself.','2018-04-27 07:47:58'),(108,'Solo: A Star Wars Story','348350','Through a series of daring escapades deep within a dark and dangerous criminal underworld, Han Solo meets his mighty future copilot Chewbacca and encounters the notorious gambler Lando Calrissian.','2018-05-23','Solo: A Star Wars Story.jpg','dNW0B0HsvVs','RandomUser','3','I have low expectations but somehow feel like this is going to come through in the end and be one of the best Star Wars movies released in the last few years.  ','2018-04-27 08:03:47'),(109,'Snowpiercer','110415','In a future where a failed global-warming experiment kills off most life on the planet, a class system evolves aboard the Snowpiercer, a train that travels around the globe via a perpetual-motion engine.','2013-08-01','Snowpiercer.jpg','7dd4pogcc4Y','RandomUser','2','Strange premise but overall a decent watch.  Chris Evans was a weird addition to this movie and I have trouble removing him from his roles as Captain America and the Jock from Not Another Teen Movie.','2018-04-27 09:12:12'),(110,'Donnie Darko','141','After narrowly escaping a bizarre accident, a troubled teenager is plagued by visions of a large bunny rabbit that manipulates him to commit a series of crimes.','2001-01-18','Donnie Darko.jpg','vijy4Oiawa8','RandomUser','4','Strange but grew on me!  Very subtle and interesting in a lot of ways also has a great soundtrack','2018-04-27 09:16:29'),(111,'Gattaca','782','Science fiction drama about a future society in the era of indefinite eugenics where humans are set on a life course depending on their DNA. The young Vincent Freeman is born with a condition that would prevent him from space travel, yet he is determined to infiltrate the GATTACA space program.','1997-09-07','Gattaca.jpg','hWjlUj7Czlk','RandomUser','3','An interesting movie set in the future where space travel is possible and gene manipulation is common place.  ','2018-04-27 09:46:12'),(112,'The Fifth Element','18','In 2257, a taxi driver is unintentionally given the task of saving a young girl who is part of the key that will ensure the survival of humanity.','1997-05-07','The Fifth Element.jpg','ZH4islqoA8o','RandomUser','3','Good story with strange implementation.  I felt like this could have been less silly and more serious but overall a good watch','2018-04-27 09:59:09'),(113,'Sunshine','1272','Fifty years into the future, the sun is dying, and Earth is threatened by arctic temperatures. A team of astronauts is sent to revive the Sun â€” but the mission fails. Seven years later, a new team is sent to finish the mission as mankindâ€™s last hope.','2007-04-05','Sunshine.jpg','r8BSlqHAhuY','RandomUser','3','A good sci-fi flick.  Been a while since the last time I watched it but I remember enjoying it and particularly enjoying the soundtrack as well.','2018-04-27 10:21:44'),(114,'Dredd','49049','In the future, America is a dystopian wasteland. The latest scourge is Ma-Ma, a prostitute-turned-drug pusher with a dangerous new drug and aims to take over the city. The only possibility of stopping her is an elite group of urban police called Judges, who combine the duties of judge, jury and executioner to deliver a brutal brand of swift justice. But even the top-ranking Judge, Dredd, discovers that taking down Ma-Ma isnâ€™t as easy as it seems in this explosive adaptation of the hugely popular comic series.','2012-09-07','Dredd.jpg','PifvRiHVSCY','RandomUser','4','So much better than the 199x Stallone version.  Very visually impressive with a good story but I would have liked to see more of the wasteland city than the inside of the peachtrees housing community.  Still very well done.','2018-04-27 10:29:29'),(115,'The Terminator','218','In the post-apocalyptic future, reigning tyrannical supercomputers teleport a cyborg assassin known as the \"Terminator\" back to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor, whose unborn son is destined to lead insurgents against 21st century mechanical hegemony. Meanwhile, the human-resistance movement dispatches a lone warrior to safeguard Sarah. Can he stop the virtually indestructible killing machine?','1984-10-26','The Terminator.jpg','CEpuUhM26k8','RandomUser','4','The classic first in series Terminator.  Not a whole lot to say here other than this is a great sci-fi flick','2018-04-27 11:38:13'),(116,'Contact','686','Contact is a science fiction film about an encounter with alien intelligence. Based on the novel by Carl Sagan the film starred Jodie Foster as the one chosen scientist who must make some difficult decisions between her beliefs, the truth, and reality.','1997-07-11','Contact.jpg','SRoj3jK37Vc','RandomUser','3','Decently good.  I did not realize this was based on Carl Sagan novel.  This ran a little too long for my liking and ended on a bit of a random note but still worth watching','2018-04-27 12:02:15'),(118,'Iron Man','1726','After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.','2008-04-30','Iron Man.jpg','ofkcLgzNZGM','RandomUser','3','Not a comic book or DC/Marvel fan but this was an enjoyable movie to watch.  Robert Downey Jr did a great job here','2018-04-28 00:54:50'),(120,'The Sandlot','11528','Scotty Smalls moves to a new neighborhood with his mom and stepdad, and wants to learn to play baseball. The neighborhood baseball guru Rodriquez takes